          "name": "What’s in the box?",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What’s in every box?",
            "content": "<p>You’ll get 6–10 pieces of tackle (based on box size). This includes a mix of hardbaits, soft plastics, hooks, jigs, and sometimes exclusive drops or stickers. Every lure is full-sized, not samples. We also include tips so you know how to fish them</p>"
